OL,7,FA police officer has been found guilty
OL,8,Fof breaking his wife's back after
OL,9,Fkicking her down the stairs.
OL,11,FHuw Orphan from Barry was convicted of
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm following his
OL,13,Ftrial at Cardiff Crown Court.
OL,15,FAmy Burley, a fellow police officer,
OL,16,Fwas left with a broken back on 8
OL,17,FApril, 2020.
