OL,7,F31-year-old Orphan, who was a
OL,8,Fconstable with Gwent Police at the
OL,9,Ftime of the incident, denied
OL,10,Finflicting grievous bodily harm with
OL,11,Fintent, claiming that he had not meant
OL,12,Fto make contact with his wife nor
OL,13,Fcause her any harm.
OL,15,FHuw Orphan had been arguing with his
OL,16,Fwife by text messages beforehand the
OL,17,Fcourt heard.
