OL,7,FHe claimed that he was trying to
OL,8,F'jump' up the stairs to put some
OL,9,Fdistance between them, and that his
OL,10,Fleg accidentally made contact with Ms
OL,11,FBurley.
OL,13,FA jury at Cardiff Crown Court found
OL,14,Fhim not guilty of causing grievous
OL,15,Fbodily harm with intent but found him
OL,16,Fguilty of the lesser charge of causing
OL,17,Fgrievous bodily harm.
