OL,7,FHe was also found guilty of causing
OL,8,Factual bodily harm in a separate
OL,9,Fincident before the couple moved to
OL,10,FBarry.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, the prosecution
OL,13,Fargued that Orphan was making up his
OL,14,Fstory about accidentally catching his
OL,15,Fwife with his leg as he climbed the
OL,16,Fstairs in order to cover what he had
OL,17,Fdone.
