OL,7,FIt was the prosecution's case that he
OL,8,Fhad lost his temper and deliberately
OL,9,Fkicked his partner causing her to "fly
OL,10,Fbackwards" down the stairs and break
OL,11,Fher back.
OL,13,FOrphan denied that, saying it was his
OL,14,Fwife who had lost her temper, not him.
