OL,8,FLloyd-Clarke addressed Orphan, telling
OL,9,Fhim that a pre-sentence report would
OL,10,Fbe requested to provide her with more
OL,11,Finformation on his background prior to
OL,12,Fsentencing.
OL,14,FHe's been granted unconditional bail
OL,15,Funtil his hearing, which is due to
OL,16,Ftake place on October 25.
